snippet.title: WHAT THE GOLF? Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW!
Nintendo Switch: https://whatthegolf.com/switchstore
PC: http://whatthegolf.com/pc
Apple Arcade: http://whatthegolf.com/apple

Website: http://whatthegolf.com

Golf is always the same: perfectly round balls, 18 holes, blue sky, neatly cut grass and fancy people in nice clothes. What's not to hate?

WHAT THE GOLF? is the golf game for people who don’t play golf. Every golf course is a surprising new type of golf, some brilliant or hilarious, others simply absurd.
